<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1927-04-07T06:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1927-04-07T06:00:00-05:00" n="128" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d128">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">865.3311/52: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Fletcher</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Rome</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-04-07T12:00:00+01:00"><hi rend="italic">April 7,
                                        1927—noon</hi></date>.<lb/>[Received 12:29
                            p.m.]</dateline></opener>
                        <p>47. I have just telegraphed Mussolini expressing regret for the
                            destruction of Pinedo’s airplane. Associated Press will telegraph
                            text.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Fletcher</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>